AngularJS Client Setup and Instructions
-----------------------------------------

download zip file (weatherApp.zip) to weatherApp folder
install following node modules under \weatherApp
npm bower
npm install -g gulp
npm install gulp --save-dev
npm install jshint gulp-jshint jshint-stylish gulp-imagemin gulp-concat gulp-uglify gulp-minify-css gulp-usemin gulp-cache gulp-changed gulp-rev gulp-rename gulp-notify  browser-sync del --save-dev
bower update
npm install
gulp
npm start  - Start Server before starting client, Server runs on port 3000
gulp watch - Start Client client runs on the next available ports via bowser-sync (http://localhost:3001/#!/)

(Please see attached word document WeatherAppClientSetup.docx for detailed instructions with screen shots)
